          tears of joy and hearing victorious screams of "It compiles!"
          echoing through the office...
        </p>
        <a href="/article/missing-semicolon-found" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">
          Continue reading...
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-2">
          Tags: #debugging, #javascript, #neverGiveUp
